title: Ceph Storage: Health Status
>>>>>>> upstream/master
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the health status and epoch
 of Ceph storage systems.

 The check is OK if the storage state is 'HEALTH OK', it is
 WARN if the storage state is 'HEALTH WARN' and CRIT in case
 if 'HEALTH CRIT', otherwise UNKNOWN.

 Epoch levels are configurable. Default levels are 1 and 3
 for a timerange of 30 minutes.

inventory:
 One service is created.
